---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="agentexpert.io — Build Better AI Agents">
  <div class="container">

    <section class="hero">
      <h1>Build better AI agents.</h1>
      <p>Practical roadmaps, design patterns, tips and case studies — curated by a practitioner. No fluff, no hype.</p>
      <div class="hero-by">
        <span>By <a href="/about">Zahiruddin Tavargere</a> — Senior GenAI Architect @ Dell</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="nav-cards">
      <a href="/roadmaps" class="nav-card">
        <p class="nav-card-title">Roadmaps</p>
        <p class="nav-card-desc">Structured learning paths from your first agent to production systems.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/patterns" class="nav-card">
        <p class="nav-card-title">Patterns</p>
        <p class="nav-card-desc">Proven design patterns for tool use, memory, RAG, MCP and multi-agent systems.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/tips" class="nav-card">
        <p class="nav-card-title">Tips & tricks</p>
        <p class="nav-card-desc">Bite-sized insights from real-world agent deployments at scale.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/case-studies" class="nav-card">
        <p class="nav-card-title">Case studies</p>
        <p class="nav-card-desc">Real implementations broken down: problem, architecture, and honest learnings.</p>
      </a>
    </section>

    <section class="about-strip">
      <p>A note from the author — I'm a firm believer in social learning. I owe my career to the tech community. This site is my contribution back. Everything here comes from building real agents, not from reading about them. <a href="/about">More about me →</a></p>
    </section>

    <section class="channels">
      <p class="section-label">Also find me on</p>
      <div class="channel-list">
        <a href="https://youtube.com/@adaptiveengineer" target="_blank" class="channel-link">YouTube — Adaptive Engineer ↗</a>
        <a href="https://newsletter.adaptiveengineer.com" target="_blank" class="channel-link">Newsletter — The Adaptive Engineer ↗</a>
        <a href="https://zahere.com" target="_blank" class="channel-link">Blog — zahere.com ↗</a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero { padding: 5rem 0 3.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.25; }
  .hero p { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--muted); max-width: 520px; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .hero-by { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); }
  .hero-by a { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .hero-by a:hover { color: var(--text); border-color: var(--text); }

  .nav-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 1px solid var(--border); margin: 3rem 0; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; }
  .nav-card { background: var(--bg); padding: 1.5rem; transition: background 0.15s; }
  .nav-card:hover { background: var(--surface); }
  .nav-card-title { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .nav-card-desc { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }

  .about-strip { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .about-strip p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; }
  .about-strip a { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .about-strip a:hover { color: var(--text); border-color: var(--text); }

  .section-label { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .channel-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .channel-link { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--muted); border-bottom: 1px solid transparent; width: fit-content; transition: color 0.15s; }
  .channel-link:hover { color: var(--text); }

  @media (max-width: 560px) { .nav-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .hero h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; } }
</style>
